Minister of sports Nathi Mthethwa and SAFA president Danny Jordaan will brief the media regarding the candidacy of Patrice Motsepe for CAF Presidency. Editor's note: This livestream has ended. You may watch the recording above. JOHANNESBURG - Sports Minister Nathi Mthethwa and SAFA President, Danny Jordaan briefed media at SAFA House on Monday regarding the candidacy of Patrice Motsepe for CAF Presidency.